RACE.RACE_TEXT: FAIR MEADOWS RACE 1 4F Dirt CR: 60. Claiming Purse 7150. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs. Claiming Price $10,000.
